data.actual_result: Reaction modal appears over Discord Nitro page
data.expected_result: Discord Nitro page opens closing the Reaction modal behind
data.short_description: Reaction modal appears inside the Discord Nitro section of User Settings when clicking on the Nitro icon from a user's profile opened from the Reaction modal
data.steps_to_repro: - Open the Reaction modal on a message a user with Discord Nitro has reacted to - Right-click the user and open their profile - Click on their Nitro icon
